xlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b4b9ecab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/zh-hk/software-download/windows10</a><br />\n<br />\n之後用隻usb直接用洗機重裝。裝好時你登入自己個Microsoft account, 你會發現佢已經自動幫你activate咗。<br />\n<br />\n留意你係咩版本windows你就要裝返咩版本。例如你係windows 10 professional就裝 windows 10 professional, 係home版就裝home. 唔好搞錯。"},{"pid":"0b08fc3e73239f7bae7b5c99a16b97bc9f6440ef","tid":608443,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b47fda3baee6f829e0fc038b4ceb15a9893f9e","tid":608443,"uid":49457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"我番去試下裝個windows 10 睇下可唔可以activate到先<br />\n但裝番d driver 好煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"win10 都唔駛點煩driver 喇, 本身有lan driver 就得, 擺係度就識自動搵埋其他"},{"pid":"883b92ea89a5e1e3fac6ebd426b3151e0adf304e","tid":608443,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"win手指都可以還原到啦 onj<br />\n依家win10仲可以係藍畫面直接重設系統"},{"pid":"cabf5f5bc1e2012f501922e569ad2e2a1904ddf1","tid":608443,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"其實你乜都唔識，買mac 啦"},{"pid":"58dabfdca1a6c5abbdccee266b3f82cd6b7e01d1","tid":608443,"uid":35507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cabf5f5bc1e2012f501922e569ad2e2a1904ddf1","tid":608443,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"其實你乜都唔識，買mac 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0156aeb353ebae9a2e098a63c65ecc92d86b556","tid":608443,"uid":119169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"USB囉"},{"pid":"06ad308b43d3aa523b1a3e5d73b3660c514dd655","tid":608443,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"裝linux"},{"pid":"b3fe1c0d791a7c7749232630ae74e0e76b9898aa","tid":608443,